### Monitor Liquidation Price

```python
user_state = info.user_state(address)
for pos in user_state['assetPositions']:
    p = pos['position']
    liq_px = p.get('liquidationPx')
    entry_px = float(p['entryPx'])
    if liq_px:
        distance_pct = abs(float(liq_px) - entry_px) / entry_px * 100
        log('info', 'Liquidation distance',
            coin=p['coin'],
            entry=entry_px,
            liquidation=float(liq_px),
            distance_pct=round(distance_pct, 2),
        )
```

### Get Account Summary

